## 异常处理执行插入操作
### oracle 略过异常语句，默认提交
```sql
SQL> CREATE TABLE tmp(id int);

Table created.

CREATE OR REPLACE PROCEDURE test_proc AS 
BEGIN
  INSERT INTO tmp VALUES (-1);
  INSERT INTO tmp VALUES (1/0);  -- 制造异常
  EXCEPTION
      WHEN others THEN
          INSERT INTO tmp VALUES (1); -- 插入数据-1、1
END;
  9  /

Procedure created.

SQL> CALL test_proc();

Call completed.

SQL> SELECT * FROM tmp;

        ID
----------
        -1
         1

SQL> 
```
